<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=2009_BRIT_Awards&action=edit&section=1.php.html" title="Edit section: Hosts">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Hosts">Hosts</span></h2>
<p><a href="Kylie_Minogue" title="Kylie Minogue">Kylie Minogue</a>, <a href="Mathew_Horne" title="Mathew Horne">Mathew Horne</a> and <a href="James_Corden" title="James Corden">James Corden</a> hosted the 2009 edition of the BRIT Awards, with <a href="Fearne_Cotton" title="Fearne Cotton">Fearne Cotton</a> presenting backstage. Fearne also hosted the launch party for <a href="ITV2" title="ITV2">ITV2</a> in January.</p>
<p><a href="Johnny_Vegas" title="Johnny Vegas">Johnny Vegas</a> introduced and closed the event, as well as reading out the nominees in a pre-recorded voiceover. <a href="Emma_B" title="Emma B">Emma B</a> provided the live voiceovers as the artists came to the stage.</p>
<p><a href="Rufus_Hound" title="Rufus Hound">Rufus Hound</a>, <a href="Sara_Cox" title="Sara Cox">Sara Cox</a>, <a href="Melanie_Blatt" title="Melanie Blatt">Melanie Blatt</a> and <a href="Nicole_Appleton" title="Nicole Appleton">Nicole Appleton</a> presented the Red Carpet and Encore events on ITV2.</p>
<p><a href="Alesha_Dixon" title="Alesha Dixon">Alesha Dixon</a> presented a backstage programme, screened on ITV two days after the ceremony.</p>
